projects.title: Chakra Healing
projects.description:
Chakras are Entry Gates of the Aura.
Within the physical body resides a body double, a spiritual body, that contains the Chakras. The word Chakra in Sanscrit translates to wheel or disc.

projects.title: Nature. Water. Love
projects.description: They absorb and transmit energies to and from the universe, nature, celestial entities, from people even from things.
